IN RE: Kenneth PLAISANCE NO. 2018-B-0023 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 20, 2018

ORDER

Considering the application for reconsideration filed by respondent, and the notification from the Disciplinary Board that an Order of Compliance has been received and the processing fee paid,

IT IS ORDERED that respondent be reinstated to the practice of law, pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 19.1.
